author: John Wagner
title: Trump’s Louisville rally, in three minutes
text: Trump’s Louisville rally, in three minutes   At a rally in Louisville, March 20, President Trump pledged to deliver on his campaign promises but didn’t address comments by FBI Director James B. Comey that “no information” supports Trump’s claim that former president Barack Obama ordered a wiretap on him in 2016.
